WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
A monk in a red robe sits on a log crossing a stream.

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
The surroundings are filled with green vegetation and soft light filtered through the trees.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
The monk keeps his eyes closed and hands in a prayer position.

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
Water flows slowly beneath him, creating a serene and harmonious atmosphere.

00:12.000 --> 00:14.000
A gentle breeze moves the leaves as the camera calmly approaches.

